-- India's Reliance Comm raises 48 bln rupees via share sale - sources
-- 
-- Wed Jun 25, 2014 12:37AM EDT
-- None



June 25 (Reuters) - India's Reliance Communications Ltd <RLCM.NS> has raised 48 billion rupees ($804.02 million) in its share sale that was announced on Tuesday, as the telecommunications company looks to reduce debt.

People familiar with the matter said the company received total bids of about 120 billion rupees.